<p class="">Surely, the hon. Gentleman is confusing the whole issue. This Amendment is not to substitute the term "citizen" for "British subject," but to leave out "British subject" of the United Kingdom and Colonies. Surely, his argument is beside the point.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
